                            <comment id="13903601" author="elyograg" created="Mon, 17 Feb 2014 23:41:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m inclined to go ahead and commit this to 4x and trunk, but I&apos;d like a sanity check.  This might explain some recent problems people have been having with sending lots of updates to large clouds.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13903606" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Mon, 17 Feb 2014 23:54:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13903611" author="elyograg" created="Tue, 18 Feb 2014 00:01:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the sanity check.  I&apos;ll go ahead.&lt;/p&gt;

